Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:22.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This is the enemy's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（里見蓮太郎(さとみれんたろう)）ここが敵の拠点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:26.25,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Isn't Pleiades that thing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子(ひるこ)影胤(かげたね)）プレヤデスというのは\Nあれじゃないのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ああ　間違いなさそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.92,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,it looks like it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:37.80,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,With its limbs having degenerated \Nto such a short length,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）あの極端に短く\N退化した手足では―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be able to get any food, \Nlet alone move on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エサを取るどころか―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で動くことも\Nままならないだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.18,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて やるなら今だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,If you're going to strike, \Nyou should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:49.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I was going to blow it up \Nwith plastic explosives,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プラスチック爆弾で\N爆破するつもりだったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,but my backpack went down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,川で リュックごと流されちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:55.07,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Then there's only one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\Nじゃあ 方法は１つしかないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.41,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to fight one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいうのと\N一度 戦ってみたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.21,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I shall take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:04.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Your strength alone won't be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえだけの攻撃力じゃ無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）では やろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.17,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:10.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:25.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:48.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.93,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(460,425)}#12 Crisis Point
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.36,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Rokuro Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,轆轤鹿伏鬼(ろくろかぶと)！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.19,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Endless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）エンドレス…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.48,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,...Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）スクリーム\N（蓮太郎）バースト
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（プレヤデスのうなり声）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:15.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（プレヤデスの悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.38,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子小比奈(こひな)）パパ 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…\Nうっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.50,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it! The wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷口が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 どうして!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアたちの鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバラン…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:21.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… 助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:30.83,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Looks like Aldebaran and the \Nothers have started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）どうやら―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランたちは\N移動を開始したらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,移動？ あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.65,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠(えんじゅ)！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呼び出し音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:53.73,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子(せいてんし)）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Seitenshi-sama, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子(せいてんし)）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）聖天子様 聞いてくれ\Nプレヤデスを倒した！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）聖天子様 聞いてくれ\Nプレヤデスを倒した！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.11,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I defeated Pleiades!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Now you can use missiles and fighter jets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで ミサイルも戦闘機も使える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.11,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0,0,0,,Understood. We will commence fire support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）分かりました\N火力支援を行います
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアたちの鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Good... Now if they'll just \Ncontinue to disperse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま 逃げ散ってくれれば…\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが アルデバラン!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.34,Bullet_Flashback,gado,0,0,0,,Aldebaran is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（我堂(がどう)長政(ながまさ)）ヤツは不死身だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.71,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）そんな バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（藍原(あいはら)延珠）蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あっ 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.70,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Why did you leave without saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）どうして\N黙って出ていっちゃったのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配したのだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）すまん\Nホントにすまん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:32.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.04,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう バカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm injured there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ！\Nそこはケガしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.21,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童(てんどう)木更(きさら)）里見くん\N（蓮太郎）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.76,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You took too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）もう 遅いわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, you're all safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）みんな 無事だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.02,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun... no, Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん\Nいえ 里見リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.54,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Commander Gado
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我堂団長が戦死されました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.51,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,has died in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,In accordance with article 40 \Nof the civil officer manual,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）民警マニュアル\N第40条の規定により―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.15,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,the officer with the next \Nhighest rank assumes command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に序列が高い者に\N軍団の指揮権が移譲されます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.42,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん お願い\N私たちを導いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.03,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:22.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I didn't hate you, Gado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は あんたが嫌いじゃなかったよ\N我堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:33.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ん？\Nそこにいたのか 我が友よ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.68,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Why, there you are, my comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.00,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 どういうことだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,He saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）助けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.77,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けられた？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.80,Bullet_Main,civ,0,0,0,,I saw him kill one of our \Ncomrades in the tent village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）俺は見たぞ\Nこいつは テント村で仲間を殺した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.95,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,They decided to pick a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）突然\Nケンカを売られたものでね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.53,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,so I merely gave them the fight they sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降りかかる火の粉を\N払ったまでだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.78,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,I missed you, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠 会いたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.91,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Let's cut each other, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斬り合おう 延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:07:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.77,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（片桐(かたぎり)弓月(ゆづき)）待ちなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.38,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,You guys are the enemy of all \Nof us civil officers, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたたちは\Nあたしら民警全員の敵なのよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.10,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa, can I cut them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ こいつら斬っていい？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.13,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You may kill half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）半分 殺していいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Wait! This isn't the time to argue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！\N今 争ってる場合じゃねえだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Our common enemy is the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの共通の敵は\Nガストレアだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,If you have time to fight with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで戦ってる暇があったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.36,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,think of a way to defeat as \Nmany Gastrea as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１匹でも多く敵を倒す方法を\N考えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:27.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I'll be keeping close observation of \Nyour capability as a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）君の団長としての才覚\Nじっくり見せてもらうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッフフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）うおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.80,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（薙沢彰磨(なぎさわしょうま)）大丈夫か？ 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 彰磨兄(にい)\N翠(みどり)はどうしたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shoma-nii, where's Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（布施(ふせ) 翠）ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.72,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Midori was trying to save an \NInitiator she didn't know....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:58.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）\N翠は 顔見知りのイニシエーターを\N助けようとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.08,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And then the Gastrea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）それで ガストレアに？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.66,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,A neurotoxin stole her ability to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）神経毒で体の自由を奪われ\N俺が救い出すまで―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.30,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,and the Gastrea virus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.52,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,was injected into her continually \Nuntil I managed to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアウイルスを\N注入され続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,According to Sumire-sensei's examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,菫(すみれ)先生の検査では\N彼女の体内侵食率は もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.31,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,her corrosion rate is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.28,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, kill that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）里見くん\Nその子を殺したまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:23.95,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You once fought me for the sake \Nof maintaining order in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）かつて 君は\N世界の秩序を維持するため―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と戦った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.41,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You won that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,This is the world that you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 君の望んだ世界だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.42,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You must make amends with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が始末をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.02,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（翠）リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.68,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いがあるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.43,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Please grasp a finger of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きな指を握ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.94,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Are you touching my thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親指に触れてますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）当たってんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.35,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,You didn't cheat, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ズルしませんでしたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.70,Bullet_Main,rsen,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:10.71,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Because of my ears, \NI was never needed by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 この耳のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで 誰にも\N必要とされていませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.95,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Not even my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母親でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.86,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,But then Shoma-san needed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:19.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そんな私を\N彰磨さんは必要としてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.05,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,And so did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに あなたも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The thing that'll make Shoma-nii and me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が早く回復してくれることが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.31,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,is you getting better as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と彰磨兄にとって\N一番うれしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.44,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I smell confusion from you, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リーダーからは\N“戸惑いの匂い”がします
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Confusion has a smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N戸惑いに匂いなんてあんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.31,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,It's sort of intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直感的なものなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:41.68,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Also, concerning Tendo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと もう１つ\N天童さんについてなんですけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:42.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Kisara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）木更さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I detect a very strong smell \Nof destruction from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人からは\N強い滅びの匂いがします
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:50.75,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,She is most likely very easily \Ninfluenced by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人は きっと闇に引かれやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.57,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（翠）でも…\N（蓮太郎）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.35,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,If you're the commander, Leader Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:11:01.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダーが団長なら\Nうまくやってくれると思います
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:11:00.26,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I think she'll do okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Midori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.94,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I'm relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（翠）私 安心しました\N（蓮太郎）お… おい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:05.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに行くんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.77,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,To the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お手洗いです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.77,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,You don't intend to follow me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか ついてこないですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.88,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:18.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（翠）リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.78,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,I might... take a little while in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:27.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お手洗い 少しだけ\N遅くなるかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.41,Bullet_Main,peeps,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.41,Bullet_Main,peeps,0,0,0,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）どこにいるのー？\N（片桐玉樹(たまき)）翠ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.55,Bullet_Main,some,0,0,0,,Midori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）翠ちゃーん！\N（弓月）翠ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.55,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翠ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:54.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shoma-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）彰磨兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.16,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）翠は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.73,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,didn't want to burden \Neveryone in the adjuvant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アジュバントの足を\N引っ張りたくなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:18.22,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi, let's just say that Midori ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見\N翠は逃げたことにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.99,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,This will just upset everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 動揺する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.52,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Midori and I were a lot alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）\N俺と翠は 似たもの同士だった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.77,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,We were both empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人とも 空っぽで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.49,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and our contract was pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いの孤独を\N埋め合う契約だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.19,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,to remedy each other's loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:42.75,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi, I didn't quit the Tendo Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:44.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見 俺はな\N天童流を辞めたんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.78,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I was excommunicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破門されたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.45,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,You saw it, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も見ただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.70,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,That was a technique that I modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは 俺なりの\Nアレンジを加えた技だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.36,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,But destroying the enemy from the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:56.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 相手を内部から破壊するなど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.35,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,isn't a part of the Tendo Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童流の本質から外れているとして\N師範は許さなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.21,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Our master didn't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.56,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,That's also why I became a civil officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,民警に身をやつしたのも\Nそういう理由からだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.11,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I should have been there to finish her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は俺が\N介しゃくしてやるべきだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.45,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I was her partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相棒の俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Shoma-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彰磨兄 すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.70,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,The ones who killed Midori are the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）\N翠を殺したのは ガストレアだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.21,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,If you want to mourn her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし こいつの死を\N悼んでくれるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.28,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,swear to me that you'll defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランを倒すと誓ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.08,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Stand, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）立て 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:37.60,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,If you don't do it, \Neven more brutal deaths await.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がやらなければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと むごたらしい死が\Nばらまかれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:42.55,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,We have to stop the Tokyo Area from \Ndrowning in a sea of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:43.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリアが 血の海に沈むことを\N食い止めなきゃならん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.26,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:47.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見蓮太郎！\Nお前がやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.05,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,You have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.92,Bullet_Main,civ a,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）おい 見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.72,Bullet_Main,civ b,0,0,0,,That's Commander Gado's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）あれは 我堂団長の…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm Satomi Rentaro, and I will \Nbe taking over as commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新たな団長を務めることになった\N里見蓮太郎だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警たちの怒号）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.61,Bullet_Main,civ c,0,0,0,,Hey! The Tokyo Area's done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）おい\N東京エリアは もう終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.16,Bullet_Main,civ c,0,0,0,,Let's all run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 逃げちまおうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.26,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.38,Bullet_Main,civ c,0,0,0,,What? You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ！ やる気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Anyone else have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ほかに質問あるヤツは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.93,Bullet_Main,civ b,0,0,0,,Chikaze, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）千風(ちかぜ) やっちまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:33.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.69,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,If you move even a little, \Nyour head's gonna fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとでも動いたら\N首 落ちるけど？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう風の吹き回しだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:46.25,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,This is not the ending I wanted, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）これは 私が望んだ\Nエンディングではないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Listen up! Anyone who tries to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,or threatens the peace of the \Ngroup will be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げようとしたり\N集団の輪を乱すヤツは 排除する！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm not as kind as Gado was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 我堂ほど\N甘っちょろくはないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.79,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You're going too far, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）やりすぎよ 里見くん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.44,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あれでいいんだ\N木更さんも見たろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You saw it, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Everyone was trembling in fear of the Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな ガストレアの恐怖に\N膝を屈しかけていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,At this rate, they won't be able to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ\Nあいつらは戦えない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's why, from now on, \NI'll be the one they fear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから これから先\Nあいつらが恐怖するのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.43,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,instead of the Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアじゃなく 俺にする！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:16.55,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,But... then they'll curse you, and hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…\Nみんなに忌まれて嫌われて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.34,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Then no one will be on your side, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 里見くんの味方は\N誰もいないじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:23.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And I don't need anyone... At least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いらねえよ\N少なくとも今はな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.16,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おバカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:31.12,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Even if the whole world turns against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:35.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界中が里見くんの敵になっても\N私は ずっと君の味方よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.03,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.50,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,Those are the actions of a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壬生朝霞）\Nあれでは 独裁者と同じです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.31,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,You are not meant to be a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは 団長の器ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.19,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,Nagamasa-sama would have been more—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長政様なら もっと上手に…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Gado is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我堂は もういない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:52.80,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,didn't we lose twice because \Nhis methods were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:54.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツのやり方が間違っていたから\N２度も負けたんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.89,Bullet_Main,girlie,0,0,0,,You dare ridicule Nagamasa-sama?! You lout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長政様を愚弄するか！\N下郎ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.24,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,A fiery little one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）火の玉みたいな突進だな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.88,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Did Commander Gado being ridiculed make
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我堂団長をバカにされて\N頭に血が上ったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.56,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the blood rise to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.27,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,Who are you? State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者です！\N名乗りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.67,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Nagisawa Shoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,薙沢彰磨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.78,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I've actually just lost my partner, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は 俺も相棒がいなくなってな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.63,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.03,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Want to pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？\N俺と組まないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.33,Bullet_Main,girlie,0,0,0,,I will not serve two masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二君には仕えません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:21.16,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Don't you think we could fight Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互い かりそめでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:25.75,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,more efficiently if we paired up, \Neven if only temporarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペアがいたほうが 効率的に\Nガストレアと戦えると思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:31.26,Bullet_Main,girlie,0,0,0,,You're suggesting we pair up \Nuntil Aldebaran is defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランを倒すまでの\N非正規ペアということですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.87,Bullet_Main,girlie,0,0,0,,Then I shall lend you my strength \Nfor a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の力 一時的に\Nあなたにお預けいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.40,Bullet_Main,girlie,0,0,0,,Do with it as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご自由にお使いください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）フフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヘリのローター音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.34,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Hey, Satomi-kun, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと 里見くん\Nどういうことよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I hired her as a tactician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\N戦術顧問として雇ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:17.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We need a weapons specialist if \Nwe want to defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランを倒すには\N兵器関連のスペシャリストが必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.25,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,But did it have to be Miori \Nand Shiba Heavy Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって\N未織(みおり)と司馬(しば)重工じゃなくても…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:20.99,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（司馬未織）木更\N（木更）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.14,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Maybe you aren't aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.46,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,but the Tokyo Area's in \Nreal bad shape right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:27.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）知らんやろうけど\N今の東京エリアは ひどいもんや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.52,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,No one else has the resources to back you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちらんとこ以外に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バックアップできるような\N余力ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.21,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Aldebaran's forces have started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランの軍勢も動きだしたで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,When are they expected to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）到着予想時刻は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.23,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,11 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）午後11時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So a little more than half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あと半日と少し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So, Miori...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 未織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Is there a way to defeat Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:45.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランを倒す方法は\Nあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.86,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちを誰やと思てるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:51.51,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,This is a special bomb created \Nby our engineering division,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは うちの技術開発部が作った\N特殊爆弾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.81,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the Ekpyrotic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“エキピロティック･ボム”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.04,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,EP bomb for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,略して ＥＰ爆弾や
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.64,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,It has 20 times more power \Nthan the 500 pound bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自衛隊がアルデバランに落とした\N500ポンド爆弾の20倍の威力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.18,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,that the JASDF dropped on Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.68,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Using this, you can completely \Nannihilate Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを使って\Nアルデバランを完全消滅させる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.41,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,The only thing, Satomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただな 里見ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.36,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,You can't just hit Aldebaran with this bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:13.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この爆弾 アルデバランに\Nぶつければいいってもんやない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.59,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,According to our engineers' analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの技術班の分析では―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.85,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,it has to detonate within Aldebaran's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランの体内で\Nさく裂させる必要があるんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:24.87,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,It can only destroy it using the increase \Nin power from being in a sealed state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも 密封状態で\N威力が増すのを利用して―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく 撃滅が可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So you're saying that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり お前は アルデバランの\Nバカみたいに硬い外殻に穴を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:30.06,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,going to have to blast a hole in \NAldebaran's ridiculously hard shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,throw the EP bomb into the \Nwound before it regenerates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:34.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生する前に\NＥＰ爆弾を放り込み―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.95,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and activate the bomb \Nafter the wound has healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷口が完全に塞がってから\N起爆させろと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.17,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンポーン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.68,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,How the hell are we supposed \Nto blast a hole in its shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど どうやって\N外殻に穴を開けるつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.31,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,We don't have a weapon with \Nthat kind of piercing power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな とんでもない\N貫通力を持った武器なんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.72,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.20,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Just one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）あるよ　たった１つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.57,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,that has more power and reliability \Nthan a tank cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦車砲より強力で信頼もある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.32,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Our most powerful and final weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちらの最大にして最後の武器が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:54.44,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:18:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:18:59.79,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）そっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.83,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,This plan will now be known as "Rapier's Last!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本作戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以後“レイピア･スラスト”と\N呼ぶことにする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.57,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,We'll abandon this post,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちらは ここを放棄して\N後方に陣地を構え―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.25,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,set up a camp in the rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.08,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,and face Aldebaran from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで アルデバランを迎え撃つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.39,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,The rear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.84,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,There isn't a place to set up an encampment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:15.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後方？\N陣地構築に適した場所なんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:20.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:22.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終決戦の場所は“回帰の炎”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You're going to find Aldebaran \Nwith those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あのライトで\Nアルデバランを見つけんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:31.98,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Yep. This plan hinges on \Nhow fast we can find the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）そや　今回の作戦は―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵をどれだけ早く発見するかが\N勝負の分かれ目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.36,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,We're just waiting for the batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは バッテリー待ちや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:37.15,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Right. We've asked the JASDF for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自衛隊にお願いして\N今 陸路で運んでいるところ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.22,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and they're transporting \Nthem by land as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,They're taking too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅いな\Nそろそろ配置につくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We're getting into our positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.87,Bullet_Main,civs,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）おー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Enju? It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした 延珠\N時間だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:56.13,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, do you remember the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎\N前に ここに来たとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.57,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,we came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えているか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.76,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking... This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,油断した　ここは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（少女たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.05,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.26,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Why does the Stolen Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奪われた世代は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:18.36,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,do such terrible things to the Cursed Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 呪われた子供たちに\Nひどいことをするのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:23.27,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,We just want a place in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾(わらわ)たちは この世界に\N居場所が欲しいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.33,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Everyone says that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 言ってる\N民警システムは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.39,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the civil officer system is just a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.08,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,good way for the Gastrea and \Nus to kill each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアと妾たちを殺し合わせる\N体(てい)のいいゴミ処理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.87,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,A good way to get rid of the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠 お前もそう思うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.84,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,is that what you think, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I believe that working for a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,民間警備会社は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.83,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,civil security agency is a job where I can risk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他人のために\N命を懸けることができる職業だと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.22,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,my life for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Which do you want to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は どっちを信じたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.41,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.02,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Rentaro! Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎　蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.32,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju, you don't have to decide right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠の泣き声）\N（蓮太郎）延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 結論を出すことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.59,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,But... in order for you to have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど お前が本気で―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.25,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the time to truly decide whether \Nthis world is worth saving or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を救ってもいいと\N考えるまでの時間を作るためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,we need the world to keep existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を存続させなきゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.03,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（はなをすする音）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.17,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I'm all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾は もう大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:18.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.59,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）団長！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.82,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,everyone's in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:24.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員 配置についたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.72,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,It appears that you finally have all the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）分かった！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ようやく\Nカードがそろったようだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.44,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キング
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:30.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.20,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クイーン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.85,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.23,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エース
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.97,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,and joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ジョーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.88,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,The adjuvant of five pairs \Nthat I originally had in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当初 考えていた\N５組10人のアジュバント構想が―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.56,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,has finally coalesced in the eleventh hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場でなった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:48.77,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,All the preparations have \Nbeen made, Aldebaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで 準備が全て整ったぞ\Nアルデバラン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:55.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性たち）えい！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.85,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,These are all of the batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性）\Nバッテリーは これで全部です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（保脇(やすわき)卓人(たくと)）フッフフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:16.04,Bullet_Main,jerkface,0,0,0,,This will mean the end of Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで 里見蓮太郎もおしまいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:24.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:39.14,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,#13 The Ones Who Aspired to Be Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We will now eliminate the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.62,Bullet_Main,mask,0,0,0,,Yes... This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）これより 敵を排除する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.31,Bullet_Main,tina(?),0,0,0,,Target confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:35.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）これが死 これが戦争\N（ティナ）突撃 支援します
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん このままじゃ…\N（延珠）蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju... This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:40.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠　お別れだ
